      "Replication": "Disabled",
      "Description": "Allows for DesignScript code to be authored directly",
      "Code": "l;\np;\nhh;\nhi;\nc1;\nc2;\nk;\nj;\ne;\nan;\nesc;\ndes;\ncat;\nmod;\nqes;\nlt;\nht;\net;\ndi;\ndf;\n\npa  = \"Elevation\";\ni   = [2,3,4,13,19,17,15,7];\ncot = an.SetParameterByName( pa , hh );\n//---------------------------------------\nx   = [ -0.50+k ,   0    ,     0.5+k ] * l;\ny   = [  0.50,c1,c2,0,-c2,-c1,-0.5   ] * p;\n//---------------------------------------\nLP  = Point.ByCoordinates ( x<1>, y, 0 );\nLV  = List.Flatten        ( LP , 1 )[i];\nPO  = PolyCurve.ByPoints  ( LV , 1 );\nEi  = Line.ByBestFitThroughPoints(LV);\n\nmas = Mastro (mod,PO,cat,esc,des,hh,hi,l);\nPo1 = mas[0][1];\nPo2 = mas[0][2];\ncab = Estais (Po1, Po2, di, df, hi, qes);\nptc = List.Flatten(cab[3], 2);\nPista ( lt, ht , et , ptc );"
